item.text:
Accountable Health Communities Core Health-Related Social Needs Screening Questions 
Underlined answer options indicate positive responses for the associated health-related social need. 
A value greater than 10 when the numerical values for answers to questions 7-10 are summed indicates a positive screen for interpersonal safety.

option.valueString: I do not have housing (I am staying with others, in a hotel, in a shelter, living outside on the street, on a beach, in a car, abandoned building, bus or train station, or in a park)
I have housing today, but I am worried about losing housing in the future

item.text: What is your housing situation today?

option.valueString: No or not working smoke detectors

item.text: Think about the place you live. Do you have problems with any of the following? (check all that apply)
